snippet.title: Announcement Trailer - Viva Veloce
snippet.description:
Wishlist Now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2787100?utm_source=trailer

Viva Veloce is a retro top-down street racing experience with everything modernized. Race! Earn money! And be the king of the streets of Rome with your tuned, 4 wheeled, monster.

Vivaldi - La Follia
